data.enText: a small dark red soft fruit that grows on bushes

data.chText: （将舌头伸出并吹气而发出的粗鲁的声音）呸声，嘘声
data.enText: a rude sound made by sticking out the tongue and blowing
to blow a raspberry at sb

means: (将舌头伸出并吹气而发出的粗鲁的声音)呸声，嘘声

tr: a cry or noise made to express displeasure or contempt
red or black edible aggregate berries usually smaller than the related blackberries
woody brambles bearing usually red but sometimes black or yellow fruits that separate from the receptacle when ripe and are rounder and smaller than blackberries

value.def: Raspberries are small, soft, red fruit that grow on bushes.
value.tran: 悬钩子;覆盆子;木莓;山莓

value.def: If you blow a raspberry, you make a sound by putting your tongue out and blowing, in order to insult someone.

example.ex: He blows a raspberry down the telephone line and hangs up...
example.tran: 他对着电话呸了一声，然后挂断了。
他们所有人都在吐舌头发出讥笑声。

value.def: If you blow a raspberry at someone or something, you reject them completely or criticize them severely.

example.ex: ...a time to blow a modest raspberry at politics...
example.tran: 对政治稍加指责的时期
